.source
Includes source in Oberon-2.
.description
ANother Great Intuition Enhancer commodity that offers about 100 Intuition
related actions you may assign to multiple arbitrary hotkeys.  Arbitrary
DOS commands and input event data may be assigned to the hotkeys too.
Furthermore, Angie includes automatic window hunting, auto ActiveWinTask
priority increment, 'TWA' type window remembering, auto DefPubScreen
definition, etc.  Angie comes with a comfortable Intuition user interface.
Giftware.  
